headline: Booking Holdings, Etraveli Group Extend Partnership for 8 Years to Enhance Global Flight Offerings
summary: Booking Holdings Inc. (NASDAQ:BKNG) is one of the best QQQ stocks to buy according to hedge funds. Earlier on June 12, Booking Holdings announced an 8-year extension of its commercial partnership with Etraveli Group.
